[24.673949, "o", "[programmer] [profile=board-autodetect] podman run --rm -v /home/thecharge/workspace/sndv-hdl:/workspace -w /workspace --device /dev/bus/usb ts2v-gowin-oss:latest bash -lc set -e; openFPGALoader --scan-usb; openFPGALoader --external-flash --write-flash --verify -r -b tangnano20k /workspace/.artifacts/calc_uart/hw.fs\r\n[profile=board-autodetect]\r\nempty\r\nBus device vid:pid       probe_type manufacturer serial     product\r\n005 039    0x0403:0x6010 FTDI2232   SIPEED       2025012315 USB Debugger\r\nempty\r\nwrite to flash\r\nJtag frequency : requested 6.00MHz    -> real 6.00MHz   \r\nParse file Parse /workspace/.artifacts/calc_uart/hw.fs: \r\nDone\r\nDONE\r\nafter program flash: displayReadReg 00006020\r\n\tMemory Erase\r\n\tDone Final\r\n\tSecurity Final\r\nErase SRAM DONE\r\nJtag probe limited to %d MHz6000000\r\nJtag frequency : requested 10.00MHz   -> real 6.00MHz   \r\nJEDEC ID: 0xef4017\r\nDetected: Winbond W25Q64 128 sectors size: 64Mb\r\nJEDEC ID: 0xef4017\r\nDetected: Winbond W25Q64 128 sectors size: 64Mb\r\nRDSR : 0x00\r\nWIP  : 0\r\nWEL  : 0\r\nBP   : 0\r\nTB   : 0\r\nSRWD : 0\r\n00000000 00000000 00000000 00\r\nstart addr: 00000000, end_addr: 00090000\r\n\rErasing: [===============================================   ] 92.20%\r\n\rErasing: [==================================================] 99.29%\r\n\rErasing: [==================================================] 100.00%\r\n\r\nDone\r\n\rWriting: [                                                  ] 0.00%\r\n\rWriting: [===========                                       ] 21.25%\r\n\rWriting: [======================                            ] 42.40%\r\n\rWriting: [================================                  ] 63.69%\r\n\rWriting: [===========================================       ] 84.94%\r\n\rWriting: [==================================================] 100.00%\r\n\r\nDone\r\nVerifying write (May take time)\r\n\rReading: [===================                               ] 36.9